🔑 Idea of Grouping
We want to calculate distances only among lanterns of the same block type.
So the first step is to collect all indices for each block type.

👉 Think of it like making buckets:

Each bucket = one block type ID.

Inside the bucket = all positions (indices) where that block type appears.

