🧩 DSA Pattern
Grouping by value: Collect indices of each lantern type.

Prefix sums: Use prefix sums of indices to compute left and right contributions efficiently.

Formula:

Left contribution = idx[i] * i - sum(left indices)

Right contribution = (sum(right indices)) - idx[i] * countRight

Complexity: O(n) overall, efficient for n up to 10^5.

